Luzbel/Attillla::

Luzbel and Attilla landed around and Luzbel said to Preborn "Units 
Luzbel and Attilla ready to training"

--- In nbwrpg@y..., "CYBERWOLF4" <cyberwolf4@p...> wrote:
> Prebon stood straight in a respectfull pose. "Trainer unit Prebon 
at your service." He fealt insulted at being called an Earthling they 
were all squishy piles of flesh that he detested for thier weaknesses.
> 
> "I do not wish a conflict with you either but it is our custom to 
bear our arms in a show of respect for each others full strength." 
the trainer held his arms forward holding his constrictor rifle and 
revealing his shoulder and leg mounted rocket launchers. He knew 
there was no such custom but his scanners were ready to run a quick 
scan of the alien weapons systems. He was out gunned at least ten 
fold but he knew that a predacon would never pass up such an 
opportunity.

>       The Gantrathor III and the Slasidor kept flying, and then, 
they came across Prebon atop Mt.Fuji!  The two Carriers 
stopped....The pilots spoke.
>    
>        "Greetings, being!  Do not fire on us, we don't wish to be 
your enemies right off the bat....Or whatever you Earthlings call 
it.  My name is Rasile,"  then the other pilot on the other carrier 
said "And my name is Zanquar"
>    
>         "Yes, I am Rasile and he is Zanquar.  We are of a race 
called the Protoss, created by an ancient race known as the 
Xel'Naga.  In search of our enemies, the Zerg, we fell into a strange 
warp hole in space, and ended up here.  We wish to know who you are 
and where we are, but we wish not to break into a war with you," 
Rasile said, from his mic in the carrier high above.
